{"tid":1200633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"999熱線勿濫用","createTime":"2019-06-10T19:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T19:44:55.000Z","uid":226803,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78ab0f0809d20581eff14b4f05d397d62ede494c","tid":1200633,"uid":226803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:41:26.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲市民，999熱線應在緊急情況下使用，切勿濫用。<br />\n <br />\n本年首六個月，各總區指揮及控制中心共接聽1,073,892個來電，其中約66.2%屬需要處理的求助電話，其餘屬滋擾性或錯誤撥出。<br />\n <br />\n警方指，各警署能迅速處理大部分非緊急案件，市民需要時可直接求助。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/07/20180730/20180730_152037_609.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2018%2F07%2F20180730%2F20180730_152037_609.html&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=715b18ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/07/20180730/20180730_152037_609.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><strong>大家千奇唔好濫用警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"f60ea5f33129fa796a601d41458e8316702f8941","tid":1200633,"uid":224779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:44:55.000Z","msg":"大家唔好報警話大西北地方有事<br />\n以免分散警力"}]}